- logout clears session properly
- expired token routes back to login cleanly

### Business context
- business switcher is shown when multiple memberships exist
- switching business replaces the token
- session is rehydrated after switching
- business-scoped data refreshes after switching

### Current live data pages
- rooms page renders data or empty state
- tasks page renders data or empty state
- assignments page renders data or empty state
- shifts page renders data or empty state

